95#ifdef DEBUG
96static inline void CLRWFLGS(const char *file, size_t line);
97static inline void CLRWFLGS(const char *file, size_t line)
98{
99 printf("%s, %d: clear flags %s %zu\n", curr_pos.p_file,
100 curr_pos.p_line, file, line);
101 clrwflgs();
102 olwarn = LWARN_BAD;
103}
104
105static inline void SAVE(const char *file, size_t line);
106static inline void SAVE(const char *file, size_t line)
107{
108 if (olwarn != LWARN_BAD)
109 abort();
110 printf("%s, %d: save flags %s %zu = %d\n", curr_pos.p_file,
111 curr_pos.p_line, file, line, lwarn);
112 olwarn = lwarn;
113}
114
115static inline void RESTORE(const char *file, size_t line);
116static inline void RESTORE(const char *file, size_t line)
117{
118 if (olwarn != LWARN_BAD) {
119 lwarn = olwarn;
120 printf("%s, %d: restore flags %s %zu = %d\n", curr_pos.p_file,
121 curr_pos.p_line, file, line, lwarn);
122 olwarn = LWARN_BAD;
123 } else
124 CLRWFLGS(file, line);
125}
126#else
127#define CLRWFLGS(f, l) clrwflgs(), olwarn = LWARN_BAD
128#define SAVE(f, l) olwarn = lwarn
129#define RESTORE(f, l) (void)(olwarn == LWARN_BAD ? (clrwflgs(), 0) : (lwarn = olwarn))
130#endif

132/* unbind the anonymous struct members from the struct */
133static void
134anonymize(sym_t *s)
135{
136 for ( ; s; s = s->s_nxt)
137 s->s_styp = NULL;
138}

2728static __inline int uq_gt(uint64_t, uint64_t);

2732uq_gt(uint64_t a, uint64_t b)
2733{
2734
2735 return (a > b);
2736}

2739q_gt(int64_t a, int64_t b)
2740{
2741

2745#define q_lt(a, b) q_gt(b, a)

2747/*
2748 * Gets a node for a constant and returns the value of this constant
2749 * as integer.
2750 * Is the node not constant or too large for int or of type float,
2751 * a warning will be printed.
2752 *
2753 * toicon() should be used only inside declarations. If it is used in
2754 * expressions, it frees the memory used for the expression.
2755 */
2756static int
2757toicon(tnode_t *tn, int required)
2758{
2759 int i;
2760 tspec_t t;
2761 val_t *v;
2762
2763 v = constant(tn, required);
2764
2765 /*
2766 * Abstract declarations are used inside expression. To free
2767 * the memory would be a fatal error.
2768 * We don't free blocks that are inside casts because these
2769 * will be used later to match types.
2770 */
2771 if (tn->tn_op != CON && dcs->d_ctx != ABSTRACT)
2772 tfreeblk();
2773
2774 if ((t = v->v_tspec) == FLOAT || t == DOUBLE || t == LDOUBLE) {
2775 i = (int)v->v_ldbl;
2776 /* integral constant expression expected */
2777 error(55);
2778 } else {
2779 i = (int)v->v_quad;
2780 if (isutyp(t)) {
2781 if (uq_gt((uint64_t)v->v_quad,
2782 (uint64_t)TARG_INT_MAX)) {
2783 /* integral constant too large */
2784 warning(56);
2785 }
2786 } else {
2787 if (q_gt(v->v_quad, (int64_t)TARG_INT_MAX) ||
2788 q_lt(v->v_quad, (int64_t)TARG_INT_MIN)) {
2789 /* integral constant too large */
2790 warning(56);
2791 }
2792 }
2793 }
2794 free(v);
2795 return (i);
2796}

2798static void
2799idecl(sym_t *decl, int initflg, sbuf_t *renaming)
2800{
2801 char *s;
2802
2803 initerr = 0;
2804 initsym = decl;
2805
2806 switch (dcs->d_ctx) {
2807 case EXTERN:
2808 if (renaming != NULL) {
2809 if (decl->s_rename != NULL)
2810 LERROR("idecl(rename)");
2811
2812 s = getlblk(1, renaming->sb_len + 1);
2813 (void)memcpy(s, renaming->sb_name, renaming->sb_len + 1);
2814 decl->s_rename = s;
2815 freeyyv(&renaming, T_NAME);
2816 }
2817 decl1ext(decl, initflg);
2818 break;
2819 case ARG:
2820 if (renaming != NULL) {
2821 /* symbol renaming can't be used on function arguments */
2822 error(310);
2823 freeyyv(&renaming, T_NAME);
2824 break;
2825 }
2826 (void)decl1arg(decl, initflg);
2827 break;
2828 case AUTO:
2829 if (renaming != NULL) {
2830 /* symbol renaming can't be used on automatic variables */
2831 error(311);
2832 freeyyv(&renaming, T_NAME);
2833 break;
2834 }
2835 decl1loc(decl, initflg);
2836 break;
2837 default:
2838 LERROR("idecl(%d)", dcs->d_ctx);
2839 }
2840
2841 if (initflg && !initerr)
2842 prepinit();
2843}

2845/*
2846 * Discard all input tokens up to and including the next
2847 * unmatched right paren
2848 */
2849static void
2850ignuptorp(void)
2851{
2852 int level;
2853
2854 if (yychar < 0)
2855 yychar = yylex();
2856 freeyyv(&yylval, yychar);
2857
2858 level = 1;
2859 while (yychar != T_RPARN || --level > 0) {
2860 if (yychar == T_LPARN) {
2861 level++;
2862 } else if (yychar <= 0) {
2863 break;
2864 }
2865 freeyyv(&yylval, yychar = yylex());
2866 }
2867
2868 yyclearin;
2869}

2890#include <stdlib.h> /* needed for malloc, etc */
2891#include <string.h> /* needed for memset */
2892
2893/* allocate initial stack or double stack size, up to YYMAXDEPTH */
2894static int yygrowstack(YYSTACKDATA *data)
2895{
2896 int i;
2897 unsigned newsize;
2898 YYINT *newss;
2899 YYSTYPE *newvs;
2900#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
2901 YYLTYPE *newps;
2902#endif
2903
2904 if ((newsize = data->stacksize) == 0)
2905 newsize = YYINITSTACKSIZE;
2906 else if (newsize >= YYMAXDEPTH)
2907 return YYENOMEM;
2908 else if ((newsize *= 2) > YYMAXDEPTH)
2909 newsize = YYMAXDEPTH;
2910
2911 i = (int) (data->s_mark - data->s_base);
2912 newss = (YYINT *)realloc(data->s_base, newsize * sizeof(*newss));
2913 if (newss == 0)
2914 return YYENOMEM;
2915
2916 data->s_base = newss;
2917 data->s_mark = newss + i;
2918
2919 newvs = (YYSTYPE *)realloc(data->l_base, newsize * sizeof(*newvs));
2920 if (newvs == 0)
2921 return YYENOMEM;
2922
2923 data->l_base = newvs;
2924 data->l_mark = newvs + i;
2925
2926#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
2927 newps = (YYLTYPE *)realloc(data->p_base, newsize * sizeof(*newps));
2928 if (newps == 0)
2929 return YYENOMEM;
2930
2931 data->p_base = newps;
2932 data->p_mark = newps + i;
2933#endif
2934
2935 data->stacksize = newsize;
2936 data->s_last = data->s_base + newsize - 1;
2937
2938#if YYDEBUG
2939 if (yydebug)
2940 fprintf(stderr, "%sdebug: stack size increased to %d\n", YYPREFIX, newsize);
2941#endif
2942 return 0;
2943}
2944
2945#if YYPURE || defined(YY_NO_LEAKS)
2946static void yyfreestack(YYSTACKDATA *data)
2947{
2948 free(data->s_base);
2949 free(data->l_base);
2950#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
2951 free(data->p_base);
2952#endif
2953 memset(data, 0, sizeof(*data));
2954}
2955#else
2956#define yyfreestack(data) /* nothing */
2957#endif /* YYPURE || defined(YY_NO_LEAKS) */
2958#if YYBTYACC
2959
2960static YYParseState *
2961yyNewState(unsigned size)
2962{
2963 YYParseState *p = (YYParseState *) malloc(sizeof(YYParseState));
2964 if (p == NULL) return NULL;
2965
2966 p->yystack.stacksize = size;
2967 if (size == 0)
2968 {
2969 p->yystack.s_base = NULL;
2970 p->yystack.l_base = NULL;
2971#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
2972 p->yystack.p_base = NULL;
2973#endif
2974 return p;
2975 }
2976 p->yystack.s_base = (YYINT *) malloc(size * sizeof(YYINT));
2977 if (p->yystack.s_base == NULL) return NULL;
2978 p->yystack.l_base = (YYSTYPE *) malloc(size * sizeof(YYSTYPE));
2979 if (p->yystack.l_base == NULL) return NULL;
2980 memset(p->yystack.l_base, 0, size * sizeof(YYSTYPE));
2981#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
2982 p->yystack.p_base = (YYLTYPE *) malloc(size * sizeof(YYLTYPE));
2983 if (p->yystack.p_base == NULL) return NULL;
2984 memset(p->yystack.p_base, 0, size * sizeof(YYLTYPE));
2985#endif
2986
2987 return p;
2988}
2989
2990static void
2991yyFreeState(YYParseState *p)
2992{
2993 yyfreestack(&p->yystack);
2994 free(p);
2995}
2996#endif /* YYBTYACC */

3000#define YYACCEPT goto yyaccept

3003#define YYVALID do { if (yyps->save) goto yyvalid; } while(0)

3005 yyps->save->save == 0) goto yyvalid; } while(0)

3008int
3009YYPARSE_DECL()
3010{
3011 int yym, yyn, yystate, yyresult;
3012#if YYBTYACC
3013 int yynewerrflag;
3014 YYParseState *yyerrctx = NULL;
3015#endif /* YYBTYACC */
3016#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3017 YYLTYPE yyerror_loc_range[3]; /* position of error start/end (0 unused) */
3018#endif
3019#if YYDEBUG
3020 const char *yys;
3021
3022 if ((yys = getenv("YYDEBUG")) != 0)
3023 {
3024 yyn = *yys;
3025 if (yyn >= '0' && yyn <= '9')
3026 yydebug = yyn - '0';
3027 }
3028 if (yydebug)
3029 fprintf(stderr, "%sdebug[<# of symbols on state stack>]\n", YYPREFIX);
3030#endif
3031#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3032 memset(yyerror_loc_range, 0, sizeof(yyerror_loc_range));
3033#endif
3034
3035#if YYBTYACC
3036 yyps = yyNewState(0); if (yyps == 0) goto yyenomem;
3037 yyps->save = 0;
3038#endif /* YYBTYACC */
3039 yym = 0;
3040 yyn = 0;
3041 yynerrs = 0;
3042 yyerrflag = 0;
3043 yychar = YYEMPTY;
3044 yystate = 0;
3045
3046#if YYPURE
3047 memset(&yystack, 0, sizeof(yystack));
3048#endif
3049
3050 if (yystack.s_base == NULL && yygrowstack(&yystack) == YYENOMEM) goto yyoverflow;
3051 yystack.s_mark = yystack.s_base;
3052 yystack.l_mark = yystack.l_base;
3053#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3054 yystack.p_mark = yystack.p_base;
3055#endif
3056 yystate = 0;
3057 *yystack.s_mark = 0;
3058
3059yyloop:
3060 if ((yyn = yydefred[yystate]) != 0) goto yyreduce;
3061 if (yychar < 0)
3062 {
3063#if YYBTYACC
3064 do {
3065 if (yylvp < yylve)
3066 {
3067 /* we're currently re-reading tokens */
3068 yylval = *yylvp++;
3069#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3070 yylloc = *yylpp++;
3071#endif
3072 yychar = *yylexp++;
3073 break;
3074 }
3075 if (yyps->save)
3076 {
3077 /* in trial mode; save scanner results for future parse attempts */
3078 if (yylvp == yylvlim)
3079 { /* Enlarge lexical value queue */
3080 size_t p = (size_t) (yylvp - yylvals);
3081 size_t s = (size_t) (yylvlim - yylvals);
3082
3083 s += YYLVQUEUEGROWTH;
3084 if ((yylexemes = (YYINT *)realloc(yylexemes, s * sizeof(YYINT))) == NULL) goto yyenomem;
3085 if ((yylvals = (YYSTYPE *)realloc(yylvals, s * sizeof(YYSTYPE))) == NULL) goto yyenomem;
3086#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3087 if ((yylpsns = (YYLTYPE *)realloc(yylpsns, s * sizeof(YYLTYPE))) == NULL) goto yyenomem;
3088#endif
3089 yylvp = yylve = yylvals + p;
3090 yylvlim = yylvals + s;
3091#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3092 yylpp = yylpe = yylpsns + p;
3093 yylplim = yylpsns + s;
3094#endif
3095 yylexp = yylexemes + p;
3096 }
3097 *yylexp = (YYINT) YYLEX;
3098 *yylvp++ = yylval;
3099 yylve++;
3100#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3101 *yylpp++ = yylloc;
3102 yylpe++;
3103#endif
3104 yychar = *yylexp++;
3105 break;
3106 }
3107 /* normal operation, no conflict encountered */
3108#endif /* YYBTYACC */
3109 yychar = YYLEX;
3110#if YYBTYACC
3111 } while (0);
3112#endif /* YYBTYACC */
3113 if (yychar < 0) yychar = YYEOF;
3114#if YYDEBUG
3115 if (yydebug)
3116 {
3117 if ((yys = yyname[YYTRANSLATE(yychar)]) == NULL) yys = yyname[YYUNDFTOKEN];
3118 fprintf(stderr, "%s[%d]: state %d, reading token %d (%s)",
3119 YYDEBUGSTR, yydepth, yystate, yychar, yys);
3120#ifdef YYSTYPE_TOSTRING
3121#if YYBTYACC
3122 if (!yytrial)
3123#endif /* YYBTYACC */
3124 fprintf(stderr, " <%s>", YYSTYPE_TOSTRING(yychar, yylval));
3125#endif
3126 fputc('\n', stderr);
3127 }
3128#endif
3129 }
3130#if YYBTYACC
3131
3132 /* Do we have a conflict? */
3133 if (((yyn = yycindex[yystate]) != 0) && (yyn += yychar) >= 0 &&
3134 yyn <= YYTABLESIZE && yycheck[yyn] == (YYINT) yychar)
3135 {
3136 YYINT ctry;
3137
3138 if (yypath)
3139 {
3140 YYParseState *save;
3141#if YYDEBUG
3142 if (yydebug)
3143 fprintf(stderr, "%s[%d]: CONFLICT in state %d: following successful trial parse\n",
3144 YYDEBUGSTR, yydepth, yystate);
3145#endif
3146 /* Switch to the next conflict context */
3147 save = yypath;
3148 yypath = save->save;
3149 save->save = NULL;
3150 ctry = save->ctry;
3151 if (save->state != yystate) YYABORT;
3152 yyFreeState(save);
3153
3154 }
3155 else
3156 {
3157
3158 /* Unresolved conflict - start/continue trial parse */
3159 YYParseState *save;
3160#if YYDEBUG
3161 if (yydebug)
3162 {
3163 fprintf(stderr, "%s[%d]: CONFLICT in state %d. ", YYDEBUGSTR, yydepth, yystate);
3164 if (yyps->save)
3165 fputs("ALREADY in conflict, continuing trial parse.\n", stderr);
3166 else
3167 fputs("Starting trial parse.\n", stderr);
3168 }
3169#endif
3170 save = yyNewState((unsigned)(yystack.s_mark - yystack.s_base + 1));
3171 if (save == NULL) goto yyenomem;
3172 save->save = yyps->save;
3173 save->state = yystate;
3174 save->errflag = yyerrflag;
3175 save->yystack.s_mark = save->yystack.s_base + (yystack.s_mark - yystack.s_base);
3176 memcpy (save->yystack.s_base, yystack.s_base, (size_t) (yystack.s_mark - yystack.s_base + 1) * sizeof(YYINT));
3177 save->yystack.l_mark = save->yystack.l_base + (yystack.l_mark - yystack.l_base);
3178 memcpy (save->yystack.l_base, yystack.l_base, (size_t) (yystack.l_mark - yystack.l_base + 1) * sizeof(YYSTYPE));
3179#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3180 save->yystack.p_mark = save->yystack.p_base + (yystack.p_mark - yystack.p_base);
3181 memcpy (save->yystack.p_base, yystack.p_base, (size_t) (yystack.p_mark - yystack.p_base + 1) * sizeof(YYLTYPE));
3182#endif
3183 ctry = yytable[yyn];
3184 if (yyctable[ctry] == -1)
3185 {
3186#if YYDEBUG
3187 if (yydebug && yychar >= YYEOF)
3188 fprintf(stderr, "%s[%d]: backtracking 1 token\n", YYDEBUGSTR, yydepth);
3189#endif
3190 ctry++;
3191 }
3192 save->ctry = ctry;
3193 if (yyps->save == NULL)
3194 {
3195 /* If this is a first conflict in the stack, start saving lexemes */
3196 if (!yylexemes)
3197 {
3198 yylexemes = (YYINT *) malloc((YYLVQUEUEGROWTH) * sizeof(YYINT));
3199 if (yylexemes == NULL) goto yyenomem;
3200 yylvals = (YYSTYPE *) malloc((YYLVQUEUEGROWTH) * sizeof(YYSTYPE));
3201 if (yylvals == NULL) goto yyenomem;
3202 yylvlim = yylvals + YYLVQUEUEGROWTH;
3203#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3204 yylpsns = (YYLTYPE *) malloc((YYLVQUEUEGROWTH) * sizeof(YYLTYPE));
3205 if (yylpsns == NULL) goto yyenomem;
3206 yylplim = yylpsns + YYLVQUEUEGROWTH;
3207#endif
3208 }
3209 if (yylvp == yylve)
3210 {
3211 yylvp = yylve = yylvals;
3212#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3213 yylpp = yylpe = yylpsns;
3214#endif
3215 yylexp = yylexemes;
3216 if (yychar >= YYEOF)
3217 {
3218 *yylve++ = yylval;
3219#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3220 *yylpe++ = yylloc;
3221#endif
3222 *yylexp = (YYINT) yychar;
3223 yychar = YYEMPTY;
3224 }
3225 }
3226 }
3227 if (yychar >= YYEOF)
3228 {
3229 yylvp--;
3230#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3231 yylpp--;
3232#endif
3233 yylexp--;
3234 yychar = YYEMPTY;
3235 }
3236 save->lexeme = (int) (yylvp - yylvals);
3237 yyps->save = save;
3238 }
3239 if (yytable[yyn] == ctry)
3240 {
3241#if YYDEBUG
3242 if (yydebug)
3243 fprintf(stderr, "%s[%d]: state %d, shifting to state %d\n",
3244 YYDEBUGSTR, yydepth, yystate, yyctable[ctry]);
3245#endif
3246 if (yychar < 0)
3247 {
3248 yylvp++;
3249#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3250 yylpp++;
3251#endif
3252 yylexp++;
3253 }
3254 if (yystack.s_mark >= yystack.s_last && yygrowstack(&yystack) == YYENOMEM)
3255 goto yyoverflow;
3256 yystate = yyctable[ctry];
3257 *++yystack.s_mark = (YYINT) yystate;
3258 *++yystack.l_mark = yylval;
3259#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3260 *++yystack.p_mark = yylloc;
3261#endif
3262 yychar = YYEMPTY;
3263 if (yyerrflag > 0) --yyerrflag;
3264 goto yyloop;
3265 }
3266 else
3267 {
3268 yyn = yyctable[ctry];
3269 goto yyreduce;
3270 }
3271 } /* End of code dealing with conflicts */
3272#endif /* YYBTYACC */
3273 if (((yyn = yysindex[yystate]) != 0) && (yyn += yychar) >= 0 &&
3274 yyn <= YYTABLESIZE && yycheck[yyn] == (YYINT) yychar)
3275 {
3276#if YYDEBUG
3277 if (yydebug)
3278 fprintf(stderr, "%s[%d]: state %d, shifting to state %d\n",
3279 YYDEBUGSTR, yydepth, yystate, yytable[yyn]);
3280#endif
3281 if (yystack.s_mark >= yystack.s_last && yygrowstack(&yystack) == YYENOMEM) goto yyoverflow;
3282 yystate = yytable[yyn];
3283 *++yystack.s_mark = yytable[yyn];
3284 *++yystack.l_mark = yylval;
3285#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3286 *++yystack.p_mark = yylloc;
3287#endif
3288 yychar = YYEMPTY;
3289 if (yyerrflag > 0) --yyerrflag;
3290 goto yyloop;
3291 }
3292 if (((yyn = yyrindex[yystate]) != 0) && (yyn += yychar) >= 0 &&
3293 yyn <= YYTABLESIZE && yycheck[yyn] == (YYINT) yychar)
3294 {
3295 yyn = yytable[yyn];
3296 goto yyreduce;
3297 }
3298 if (yyerrflag != 0) goto yyinrecovery;
3299#if YYBTYACC
3300
3301 yynewerrflag = 1;
3302 goto yyerrhandler;
3303 goto yyerrlab; /* redundant goto avoids 'unused label' warning */
3304
3305yyerrlab:
3306 /* explicit YYERROR from an action -- pop the rhs of the rule reduced
3307 * before looking for error recovery */
3308 yystack.s_mark -= yym;
3309 yystate = *yystack.s_mark;
3310 yystack.l_mark -= yym;
3311#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3312 yystack.p_mark -= yym;
3313#endif
3314
3315 yynewerrflag = 0;
3316yyerrhandler:
3317 while (yyps->save)
3318 {
3319 int ctry;
3320 YYParseState *save = yyps->save;
3321#if YYDEBUG
3322 if (yydebug)
3323 fprintf(stderr, "%s[%d]: ERROR in state %d, CONFLICT BACKTRACKING to state %d, %d tokens\n",
3324 YYDEBUGSTR, yydepth, yystate, yyps->save->state,
3325 (int)(yylvp - yylvals - yyps->save->lexeme));
3326#endif
3327 /* Memorize most forward-looking error state in case it's really an error. */
3328 if (yyerrctx == NULL || yyerrctx->lexeme < yylvp - yylvals)
3329 {
3330 /* Free old saved error context state */
3331 if (yyerrctx) yyFreeState(yyerrctx);
3332 /* Create and fill out new saved error context state */
3333 yyerrctx = yyNewState((unsigned)(yystack.s_mark - yystack.s_base + 1));
3334 if (yyerrctx == NULL) goto yyenomem;
3335 yyerrctx->save = yyps->save;
3336 yyerrctx->state = yystate;
3337 yyerrctx->errflag = yyerrflag;
3338 yyerrctx->yystack.s_mark = yyerrctx->yystack.s_base + (yystack.s_mark - yystack.s_base);
3339 memcpy (yyerrctx->yystack.s_base, yystack.s_base, (size_t) (yystack.s_mark - yystack.s_base + 1) * sizeof(YYINT));
3340 yyerrctx->yystack.l_mark = yyerrctx->yystack.l_base + (yystack.l_mark - yystack.l_base);
3341 memcpy (yyerrctx->yystack.l_base, yystack.l_base, (size_t) (yystack.l_mark - yystack.l_base + 1) * sizeof(YYSTYPE));
3342#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3343 yyerrctx->yystack.p_mark = yyerrctx->yystack.p_base + (yystack.p_mark - yystack.p_base);
3344 memcpy (yyerrctx->yystack.p_base, yystack.p_base, (size_t) (yystack.p_mark - yystack.p_base + 1) * sizeof(YYLTYPE));
3345#endif
3346 yyerrctx->lexeme = (int) (yylvp - yylvals);
3347 }
3348 yylvp = yylvals + save->lexeme;
3349#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3350 yylpp = yylpsns + save->lexeme;
3351#endif
3352 yylexp = yylexemes + save->lexeme;
3353 yychar = YYEMPTY;
3354 yystack.s_mark = yystack.s_base + (save->yystack.s_mark - save->yystack.s_base);
3355 memcpy (yystack.s_base, save->yystack.s_base, (size_t) (yystack.s_mark - yystack.s_base + 1) * sizeof(YYINT));
3356 yystack.l_mark = yystack.l_base + (save->yystack.l_mark - save->yystack.l_base);
3357 memcpy (yystack.l_base, save->yystack.l_base, (size_t) (yystack.l_mark - yystack.l_base + 1) * sizeof(YYSTYPE));
3358#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3359 yystack.p_mark = yystack.p_base + (save->yystack.p_mark - save->yystack.p_base);
3360 memcpy (yystack.p_base, save->yystack.p_base, (size_t) (yystack.p_mark - yystack.p_base + 1) * sizeof(YYLTYPE));
3361#endif
3362 ctry = ++save->ctry;
3363 yystate = save->state;
3364 /* We tried shift, try reduce now */
3365 if ((yyn = yyctable[ctry]) >= 0) goto yyreduce;
3366 yyps->save = save->save;
3367 save->save = NULL;
3368 yyFreeState(save);
3369
3370 /* Nothing left on the stack -- error */
3371 if (!yyps->save)
3372 {
3373#if YYDEBUG
3374 if (yydebug)
3375 fprintf(stderr, "%sdebug[%d,trial]: trial parse FAILED, entering ERROR mode\n",
3376 YYPREFIX, yydepth);
3377#endif
3378 /* Restore state as it was in the most forward-advanced error */
3379 yylvp = yylvals + yyerrctx->lexeme;
3380#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3381 yylpp = yylpsns + yyerrctx->lexeme;
3382#endif
3383 yylexp = yylexemes + yyerrctx->lexeme;
3384 yychar = yylexp[-1];
3385 yylval = yylvp[-1];
3386#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3387 yylloc = yylpp[-1];
3388#endif
3389 yystack.s_mark = yystack.s_base + (yyerrctx->yystack.s_mark - yyerrctx->yystack.s_base);
3390 memcpy (yystack.s_base, yyerrctx->yystack.s_base, (size_t) (yystack.s_mark - yystack.s_base + 1) * sizeof(YYINT));
3391 yystack.l_mark = yystack.l_base + (yyerrctx->yystack.l_mark - yyerrctx->yystack.l_base);
3392 memcpy (yystack.l_base, yyerrctx->yystack.l_base, (size_t) (yystack.l_mark - yystack.l_base + 1) * sizeof(YYSTYPE));
3393#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3394 yystack.p_mark = yystack.p_base + (yyerrctx->yystack.p_mark - yyerrctx->yystack.p_base);
3395 memcpy (yystack.p_base, yyerrctx->yystack.p_base, (size_t) (yystack.p_mark - yystack.p_base + 1) * sizeof(YYLTYPE));
3396#endif
3397 yystate = yyerrctx->state;
3398 yyFreeState(yyerrctx);
3399 yyerrctx = NULL;
3400 }
3401 yynewerrflag = 1;
3402 }
3403 if (yynewerrflag == 0) goto yyinrecovery;
3404#endif /* YYBTYACC */
3405
3406 YYERROR_CALL("syntax error");
3407#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
3408 yyerror_loc_range[1] = yylloc; /* lookahead position is error start position */
3409#endif
3410
3411#if !YYBTYACC
3412 goto yyerrlab; /* redundant goto avoids 'unused label' warning */
3413yyerrlab:
3414#endif
3415 ++yynerrs;
3416
3417yyinrecovery:
3418 if (yyerrflag < 3)
3419 {
3420 yyerrflag = 3;
3421 for (;;)
3422 {

5811 yystate = yypath->state;
5812 goto yyloop;
5813#endif /* YYBTYACC */
5814
5815yyoverflow:
5816 YYERROR_CALL("yacc stack overflow");
5817#if YYBTYACC
5818 goto yyabort_nomem;
5819yyenomem:
5820 YYERROR_CALL("memory exhausted");
5821yyabort_nomem:
5822#endif /* YYBTYACC */
5823 yyresult = 2;
5824 goto yyreturn;
5825
5826yyabort:
5827 yyresult = 1;
5828 goto yyreturn;
5829
5830yyaccept:
5831#if YYBTYACC
5832 if (yyps->save) goto yyvalid;
5833#endif /* YYBTYACC */
5834 yyresult = 0;
5835
5836yyreturn:
5837#if defined(YYDESTRUCT_CALL)
5838 if (yychar != YYEOF && yychar != YYEMPTY)
5839#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
5840 YYDESTRUCT_CALL("cleanup: discarding token", yychar, &yylval, &yylloc);
5841#else
5842 YYDESTRUCT_CALL("cleanup: discarding token", yychar, &yylval);
5843#endif /* defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED) */
5844
5845 {
5846 YYSTYPE *pv;
5847#if defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED)
5848 YYLTYPE *pp;
5849
5850 for (pv = yystack.l_base, pp = yystack.p_base; pv <= yystack.l_mark; ++pv, ++pp)
5851 YYDESTRUCT_CALL("cleanup: discarding state",
5852 yystos[*(yystack.s_base + (pv - yystack.l_base))], pv, pp);
5853#else
5854 for (pv = yystack.l_base; pv <= yystack.l_mark; ++pv)
5855 YYDESTRUCT_CALL("cleanup: discarding state",
5856 yystos[*(yystack.s_base + (pv - yystack.l_base))], pv);
5857#endif /* defined(YYLTYPE) || defined(YYLTYPE_IS_DECLARED) */
5858 }
5859#endif /* defined(YYDESTRUCT_CALL) */
5860
5861#if YYBTYACC
5862 if (yyerrctx)
5863 {
5864 yyFreeState(yyerrctx);
5865 yyerrctx = NULL;
5866 }
5867 while (yyps)
5868 {
5869 YYParseState *save = yyps;
5870 yyps = save->save;
5871 save->save = NULL;
5872 yyFreeState(save);
5873 }
5874 while (yypath)
5875 {
5876 YYParseState *save = yypath;
5877 yypath = save->save;
5878 save->save = NULL;
5879 yyFreeState(save);
5880 }
5881#endif /* YYBTYACC */
5882 yyfreestack(&yystack);
5883 return (yyresult);
5884}
